description: The pace has dropped off and although talks continue the latest Brexit deadline is about to broken.
title: Brexit talks; Has US election slowed down trade negotiations?
title_page: Brexit talks; Has US election slowed down trade negotiations? - BBC News
maintext: Apart from anything else, the UK is not displaying signs of wanting to pursue a no-deal strategy. Of course anything is possible but, if that had been the plan, why return to the talks at all after the prime minister's very public walk-away last month?
